This paper deals with the problem of image cropping, which is a common task in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new benchmark and an efficient model, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques, respectively. Hence, it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
